raw.dow_prd_benefits_html:
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Low carbon footprint process, low aquatic toxicity&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Readily bio-degradable: &amp;gt; 99% bio derived&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;exhibits &amp;gt; 60 percent biodegradation within 28 days per OECD 301F&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Doesn’t contain EO and 1,4 dioxane&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No intentionally added sulfate, suitable for non-sulfate based system&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Vegan, Non-GMO&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Milder vs. traditional surfactants&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Ability to emulsify oils&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Effective solubilization of essential oils/fragrances&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Easy to handle, cold processable&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Suitable for clear system&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Highly concentrated, flexible to fine-tuned properties&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Low foaming impact – foaming can be improved by combination with Amino-acid surfactants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

