raw.dow_prd_benefits_html:
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Unprimed instant adhesion to a variety of engineered plastics i.e. PA, PBT.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Excellent shelf-life stability&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Self-lubricating&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fast curing for short cycle times&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Excellent process performance in a wide temperature range&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;30 Shore A hardness&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;2% oil filled&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No post-cure required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

